name: UCSF - School of Dentistry
description: UCSF School of Dentistry has educated the leading practitioners, scholars and faculty members of each generation. As a leading institution of oral and craniofacial health, the educational programs have grown to include, in addition to the DDS programs, an array of MS and PhD, post-graduate and residency programs.
